ize: 12px;\n      color: #888;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .footer a {\n      color: #FF6B35;\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 600px) {\n      .container {\n        padding: 20px 15px;\n      }\n      h2 {\n        font-size: 20px;\n      }\n      .valuation-number {\n        font-size: 24px;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"header\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #FF6B35; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;\">SpaceX IPO Insider</p>\n      <h1 class=\"logo\">🚀</h1>\n      <p style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #c0c0c0;\">Weekly IPO Tracker Report</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2>SpaceX IPO Week of 2026-04-09</h2>\n\n    <p>Welcome to this week's SpaceX IPO Insider report. Below are the latest developments in SpaceX's journey toward going public.</p>\n\n    <div class=\"highlights\">\n      <h3 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 18px;\">📰 Top Headlines</h3>\n      \n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35; background-color: #1a1a2e;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 16px;\">How the math works on a $1.75 trillion SpaceX valuation | Reuters</h4>\n        <p style=\"color: #c0c0c0; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;\">Elon Musk’s SpaceX is seeking a $1.75 trillion valuation in its forthcoming initial public offering. How far into the stratosphere is that?</p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/how-math-works-175-trillion-spacex-valuation-2026-04-08/\" style=\"color: #FF6B35; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;\">Read more →</a>\n      </div>\n    \n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35; background-color: #1a1a2e;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 16px;\">Elon Musk SpaceX IPO: $2 Trillion Valuation Push Explained - Bloomberg</h4>\n        <p style=\"color: #c0c0c0; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;\">Its <strong>$2 trillion valuation</strong> leans heavily on AI hype.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/elon-musk-spacex-ipo-2-trillion-valuation-push-explained\" style=\"color: #FF6B35; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;\">Read more →</a>\n      </div>\n    \n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35; background-color: #1a1a2e;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 16px;\">This Stock Is the Best Way to Buy Into SpaceX Before Its IPO, but Could You Be Better Off Waiting? | The Motley Fool</h4>\n        <p style=\"color: #c0c0c0; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;\">This company is set to be a major shareholder of the blockbuster IPO. ... <strong>SpaceX confidentially filed to go public via an initial public offering (IPO).</strong></p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/04/08/stock-best-way-buy-spacex-before-ipo-wait/\" style=\"color: #FF6B35; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;\">Read more →</a>\n      </div>\n    \n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35; background-color: #1a1a2e;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 16px;\">Elon Musk says SpaceX is bumping Starship's 2026 debut once again</h4>\n        <p style=\"color: #c0c0c0; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;\">SpaceX chief Elon Musk said the commercial spaceflight company is <strong>bumping the 2026 debut launch of its massive Starship rocket yet again</strong>.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://eu.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2026/04/08/spacex-delays-starship-elon-musk/89499458007/\" style=\"color: #FF6B35; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;\">Read more →</a>\n      </div>\n    \n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35; background-color: #1a1a2e;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 16px;\">SpaceX Outlines IPO Details, Targets Early June Roadshow - NYC Today</h4>\n        <p style=\"color: #c0c0c0; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>The company plans to launch its IPO roadshow in early June 2026</strong>. A private aerospace manufacturer and space transportation services company founded by Elon Musk. The Chief Financial Officer of SpaceX.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/us/ny/new-york/news/2026/04/07/spacex-outlines-ipo-details-targets-early-june-roadshow/\" style=\"color: #FF6B35; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;\">Read more →</a>\n      </div>\n    \n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"valuation-box\">\n      <h4>Current Valuation</h4>\n      <div class=\"valuation-number\">~$350B</div>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px;\">Based on latest secondary market transactions and investor rounds.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background-color: #16213e; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n      <h4 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Key Angle</h4>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: #e0e0e0;\">SpaceX Starship progress accelerates IPO timeline expectations</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background-color: #0f3460; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n      <h4 style=\"color: #FF6B35; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;\">IPO Timeline</h4>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: #e0e0e0;\">SpaceX is expected to go public in <strong>Q4 2026</strong>. Starlink IPO expected to precede SpaceX by 6-12 months. SEC filing anticipated Q2-Q3 2026.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n      <a href=\"https://spacex-ipo-tracker.com\" class=\"cta-button\">View Full Tracker →</a>\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0;\">\n        You're receiving this because you subscribed to SpaceX IPO Insider newsletter.\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0;\">\n        <a href=\"https://spacex-ipo-tracker.com\">spacex-ipo-tracker.com</a> | \n        <a href=\"#unsubscribe\">Unsubscribe</a>\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #666;\">\n        ⚠️ Disclaimer: This is informational content only. Not financial advice. Always consult with a financial advisor before investing.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
